    .vf-btns button { cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid #38bdf8; background: transparent; color: #38bdf8; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 4px; transition: 0.3s; margin-left: 5px;}
    .correct-vf { background: #22c55e !important; color: white !important; border-color: #22c55e !important; }
    .wrong-vf { background: #ef4444 !important; color: white !important; border-color: #ef4444 !important; }
</style>
<div class="vf-box">
<h3 style="color: #38bdf8; text-align: center;">🛑 FILTRO DE VERACIDAD ESTADÍSTICA</h3>
<p style="font-size: 0.9em; text-align: center;">¿Son estas afirmaciones correctas para el algoritmo?</p>
<div class="vf-item"><span>1. La varianza puede ser un número negativo.</span>
<div class="vf-btns"><button onclick="checkVF(this, false)">V</button> <button onclick="checkVF(this, true)">F</button></div>
</div>
<div class="vf-item"><span>2. Si todos los datos son iguales, la desviación típica es 0.</span>
<div class="vf-btns"><button onclick="checkVF(this, true)">V</button> <button onclick="checkVF(this, false)">F</button></div>
</div>
<div class="vf-item"><span>3. El Coeficiente de Variación tiene las mismas unidades que la media.</span>
<div class="vf-btns"><button onclick="checkVF(this, false)">V</button> <button onclick="checkVF(this, true)">F</button></div>
</div>
</div>
<p>
<script>
    function checkVF(btn, isCorrect) {
        if(isCorrect) { btn.className = 'correct-vf'; } 
        else { btn.className = 'wrong-vf'; }
    }
</script>
</p>","textFeedbackInput":"Mostrar retroalimentación","textFeedbackTextarea":""}

{"ideviceId":"idevice-1775647300318-y3m0h1idd","textInfoDurationInput":"","textInfoDurationTextInput":"Duración","textInfoParticipantsInput":"","textInfoParticipantsTextInput":"Agrupamiento","textTextarea":"<style>
    .calc-box { font-family: 'Consolas', monospace; max-width: 700px; margin: 20px auto; background: #000; border: 2px solid #00ff95; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; color: #00ff95; }
    .step-input { background: #111; border: 1px solid #00ff95; color: white; width: 60px; text-align: center; }
</style>
<div class="calc-box">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">🔢 CASO 03: TIEMPO DE RESPUESTA (ms)</h3>
<p>Datos: [ 2, 4, 6, 8 ] | Media ($\bar{x}$) = 5</p>
<div style="line-height: 2;">1. Suma de cuadrados $(x_i - \bar{x})^2$: <br />$(2-5)^2 + (4-5)^2 + (6-5)^2 + (8-5)^2 = 9 + 1 + 1 + 9 = $ <input type="number" class="step-input q_disp" data-ans="20" /> <br />2. Varianza ($S^2 = 20 / 4$): <input type="number" class="step-input q_disp" data-ans="5" /> <br />3. Desviación Típica ($S = \sqrt{5}$ aprox.):<select class="step-input q_disp" data-ans="2.24" style="width: auto;">
<option value="">--?--</option>
<option value="2.24">2.24</option>
<option value="5.00">5.00</option>
<option value="1.41">1.41</option>
</select></div>
<p id="msg_disp" style="display: none; color: white; background: #008855; padding: 5px; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center;">SISTEMA CALIBRADO ✅</p>
</div>
<p>
<script>
    (function(){
        const ins = document.querySelectorAll('.q_disp');
        ins.forEach(i => { i.addEventListener('change', function(){
            if(this.value == this.getAttribute('data-ans')){ this.style.borderColor='#0f0'; }
            else { this.style.borderColor='#f00'; }
            if(Array.from(ins).every(x => x.value == x.getAttribute('data-ans'))){ document.getElementById('msg_disp').style.display='block'; }
        });});
    })();
</script>
</p>","textFeedbackInput":"Mostrar retroalimentación","textFeedbackTextarea":""}

{"ideviceId":"idevice-1775647403334-cnsqynimd","textInfoDurationInput":"","textInfoDurationTextInput":"Duración","textInfoParticipantsInput":"","textInfoParticipantsTextInput":"Agrupamiento","textTextarea":"<div style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; max-width: 750px; margin: 20px auto; background: #1a1a1a; border: 2px solid #ffcc00; border-radius: 10px; padding: 25px; color: #ffcc00; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);">
